Git Private Data

Removes and adds confidential data when Git either adds a file or does a checkout.

Uses the Git Smudge and Clean feature See http://progit.org/book/ch7-2.html

Define the information to be hidden in smudge.regex

NB Confidential data is stored in smudge.values -- do not add that to your repo!!!

